{"tid":1565692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再叫人唔好唱歌","createTime":"2019-09-13T08:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T18:49:07.000Z","uid":306766,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"85530c23f2af8e48ebd356f2762f7b051633221f","tid":1565692,"uid":306766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:57:09.000Z","msg":"唱歌有咩問題？<br />\n成日叫人唔好唱<br />\n最緊要唱完，星期六日既活動大家會出黎。<br />\n我唔明啲人點解叫人唔好唱歌。<br />\n如果再有人叫唔好唱歌之類，試圖分化大家活動之類，請你自己諗為咩要咁做，同叫人唔好唱有咩好處。<br />\n而唱歌會帶來咩壞處，<br />\n如果講唔出，你唔好怪人懷疑你。<br />\n同時大家要對依啲post有警覺，好大可能分化post。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddecc7387f7c016fa303a39344ec65e3e7723d9b","tid":1565692,"uid":306766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c3e67aeebe43921bbd7ea17d24dbace92c10dbec","tid":1565692,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85530c23f2af8e48ebd356f2762f7b051633221f","tid":1565692,"uid":306766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:57:09.000Z","msg":"唱歌有咩問題？<br />\n成日叫人唔好唱<br />\n最緊要唱完，星期六日既活動大家會出黎。<br />\n我唔明啲人點解叫人唔好唱歌。<br />\n如果再有人叫唔好唱歌之類，試圖分化大家活動之類，請你自己諗為咩要咁做，同叫人唔好唱有咩好處。<br />\n而唱歌會帶來咩壞處，<br />\n如果講唔出，你唔好怪人懷疑你。<br />\n同時大家要對依啲post有警覺，好大可能分化post。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" c