港人權問題剔除出中美貿易談判的議程！<br />\n人權法？香港人玩得咁開心，都有國歌啦，唔駛啦！"},{"pid":"560605615533eb610e1368653d41972fa9e92995","tid":1565692,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:42:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"26419ad07c1158976550f3447773b85714fd2b78","tid":1565692,"uid":306766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f9a0e7749285fd69828a9755ad287b20b30946e","tid":1565692,"uid":252596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:49:24.000Z","msg":"多謝你哋9唱榮光HI香港。<br />\n18區嘉年華，顯示香港歌舞昇平，好太平。<br />\n美國決定將香港人權問題剔除出中美貿易談判的議程！<br />\n人權法？香港人玩得咁開心，都有國歌啦，唔駛啦！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:49:07.000Z","msg":"我明白通過人權法好重要，而通過人權法，爭取議會支持唔係好啲？<br />\n仲有佢唔放落貿易談判度，會唔會影響人權法通過？依個我唔知。<br />\n但如果佢唔將人權法bundle 貿易談判議程會唔會有佢好處？standalone 咁處理人權法會唔會快啲？ 好似新疆人權法咁，佢都冇bundle 貿易談判<br />\n總之就抗爭唔好單一化<br />\n今晚我見到有人拎美國旗同唱美國國歌，有人跟著唱。我會支持，因為大家係向同一目標。我地係需要互相提醒，互相俾意見。"}]}